1
00:00:00,100 --> 00:00:05,270

2
00:00:05,276 --> 00:00:10,045

3
00:00:37,299 --> 00:00:39,742
 The warrant is out.

4
00:00:45,716 --> 00:00:50,186
 We won't get a second chance. Let's give them a show.

5
00:00:57,594 --> 00:01:02,123
Chairwoman, there is something you need to see.

6
00:01:20,036 --> 00:01:25,089
Mrs. Yoon, you're under arrest for bribery, embezzlement, and violation of the act

7
00:01:25,089 --> 00:01:28,058
on the prevention of flight of domestic property.

8
00:01:32,607 --> 00:01:36,345
Mrs. Yoon, is your husband aware of this situation?

9
00:01:36,407 --> 00:01:38,712
Is he aware of the charges you're being arrested for?

10
00:01:38,782 --> 00:01:42,410
How do you feel, Mrs. Yoon?

11
00:01:42,410 --> 00:01:45,550
 Leave the way!

12
00:01:49,888 --> 00:01:54,162
We have to hurry before the reporters storm in.

13
00:01:59,186 --> 00:02:01,697
It's him!

14
00:02:01,697 --> 00:02:04,461
Director Yoon Jae Hee was arrested at the Sungjin Gallery.

15
00:02:04,461 --> 00:02:05,763
Have you heard the news?

16
00:02:05,829 --> 00:02:08,710
Is it true that you're not on good terms with Mrs. Yoon?

17
00:02:08,710 --> 00:02:12,850
- Did you know or not? 
 - Please give a comment!

18
00:02:12,850 --> 00:02:15,689
- One word, please! 
 - Just a moment!

19
00:02:15,689 --> 00:02:19,100
- Are you involved in any of this? 
 - One comment, please.

20
00:02:19,100 --> 00:02:21,590
Mr. President!

21
00:03:13,521 --> 00:03:15,643
What is happening?

22
00:03:15,693 --> 00:03:19,279
Wasn't the warrant going to be denied?

23
00:03:48,863 --> 00:03:50,625
 This morning, Seoul Central District Court issued

24
00:03:50,625 --> 00:03:54,104
 an arrest warrant for Yoon Jae Hee.

25
00:03:54,142 --> 00:03:56,251
 Judge Moon, who approved the warrant,

26
00:03:56,251 --> 00:03:59,429
 stated that the evidence for the charges

27
00:03:59,429 --> 00:04:03,873
 are sufficient to put her under custody.

28
00:04:03,873 --> 00:04:05,649
The charges for her arrest

29
00:04:05,728 --> 00:04:09,744
 include bribery, embezzlement,

30
00:04:09,744 --> 00:04:14,480
 violation of the act on the prevention of flight of domestic property, and

31
00:04:14,480 --> 00:04:16,165
 concealment of criminal proceeds.

32
00:04:16,165 --> 00:04:20,346
 Director Yoon did not request a pre-warrant hearing,

33
00:04:20,346 --> 00:04:25,925
 and it is speculated that she might plead guilty for the charges.

34
00:04:26,916 --> 00:04:29,826
Have you still not made up your mind?

35
00:04:32,682 --> 00:04:34,706
Joon Hyeok.

36
00:04:36,151 --> 00:04:38,347
What is the problem?

37
00:04:41,361 --> 00:04:44,407
I told her I'd forgive her.

38
00:04:44,407 --> 00:04:48,435
I told her I'd forgive her so we could start over.

39
00:04:48,464 --> 00:04:50,493
Why did you?

40
00:04:51,595 --> 00:04:58,465
Were you trying to use her wrongdoings to cover up your own?

41
00:04:58,465 --> 00:05:03,139
It's not that. She did everything intentionally.

42
00:05:03,139 --> 00:05:05,396
I only made a mistake.

43
00:05:05,396 --> 00:05:08,918
There are plenty who have done the same thing that I did.

44
00:05:08,918 --> 00:05:12,715
Why do I have to suffer when most get away with it?

45
00:05:19,252 --> 00:05:23,194
I didn't know you were so weak.

46
00:05:24,189 --> 00:05:26,814
For your own sake,

47
00:05:26,814 --> 00:05:30,282
you should give up running for President.

48
00:05:39,643 --> 00:05:42,696
Summon the referential witnesses.

49
00:05:42,756 --> 00:05:45,598
Give Seo Han Sook a confrontation with Yoon Jae Hee.

50
00:05:45,607 --> 00:05:47,672
If their accounts don't match,

51
00:05:47,707 --> 00:05:54,017
request a search and seizure warrant and get everything in their secret files.

52
00:05:54,105 --> 00:05:56,959
Yes, Sir.

53
00:05:58,929 --> 00:06:01,265

54
00:06:01,265 --> 00:06:03,912

55
00:06:14,912 --> 00:06:18,328

56
00:06:28,817 --> 00:06:32,982
 This has the list of those responsible

57
00:06:32,982 --> 00:06:36,219
 for the Hyeongsan-dong tragedy.

58
00:06:38,321 --> 00:06:42,385
 I'll let you decide whether to report this or not.

59
00:06:52,451 --> 00:06:55,551
This is no time for golf practice.

60
00:06:59,614 --> 00:07:04,994
We'd better stay on the low before we find out

61
00:07:04,994 --> 00:07:07,623
which boat will be safer to take.

62
00:07:07,623 --> 00:07:09,331
What?

63
00:07:10,697 --> 00:07:13,373
What do you think will happen

64
00:07:13,373 --> 00:07:17,813
if Cho Kang Hyeon takes a hold of the secret files of the Sungjin family?

65
00:07:33,496 --> 00:07:37,716
Congressmen Min and Kwak are not answering calls.

66
00:07:53,260 --> 00:07:54,722

67
00:07:54,722 --> 00:07:57,222

68
00:08:09,308 --> 00:08:12,526
 That "hope" you speak of,

69
00:08:12,526 --> 00:08:14,797
 who is it for?

70
00:08:34,323 --> 00:08:36,685
 Just because I'm a bastard,

71
00:08:37,502 --> 00:08:41,706
 just because I am my father's son,

72
00:08:43,633 --> 00:08:50,165
 I've been the object of ridicule all my life, and that's how I know

73
00:08:50,190 --> 00:08:53,002
 how it feels to be discriminated.

74
00:08:54,805 --> 00:09:00,217
 I don't want anyone to suffer from discrimination like I did.

75
00:09:01,657 --> 00:09:07,082
 And that's the world I want to make.

76
00:09:07,082 --> 00:09:14,495
 Joon Hyeok, let's not trample on other people's dreams,

77
00:09:14,527 --> 00:09:17,752
 or pretend to know their pain,

78
00:09:17,752 --> 00:09:20,296
 or take advantage of their misery.

79
00:09:21,364 --> 00:09:24,122
 Let's stop living like that. Okay?

80
00:09:46,712 --> 00:09:51,547
I think we'll have to brace ourselves for an investigation.

81
00:09:51,547 --> 00:09:54,236
Cho Kang Hyeon is one of the dirtiest bastards out there.

82
00:09:54,236 --> 00:09:56,337
If we blow one thing in our secret files,

83
00:09:56,426 --> 00:09:59,102
his career will be ruined for good.

84
00:09:59,102 --> 00:10:01,638
That might be a dangerous move

85
00:10:01,638 --> 00:10:06,601
when we don't know exactly how much information Jae Hee has given him.

86
00:10:06,644 --> 00:10:08,120
He could counterattack.

87
00:10:08,191 --> 00:10:10,470
SVP Kim of the legal team advised that

88
00:10:10,487 --> 00:10:15,206
it is likely that they accused her for more than what the evidence suggests.

89
00:10:15,206 --> 00:10:19,656
They're probably aiming to expand the investigation early on

90
00:10:19,656 --> 00:10:23,803
so that they can request a search and seizure warrant

91
00:10:24,637 --> 00:10:28,508
or summon us as referential witnesses.

92
00:10:28,512 --> 00:10:30,926
So Jae Hee is only the bait,

93
00:10:30,973 --> 00:10:34,405
and they're actually coming after Mother.

94
00:10:36,709 --> 00:10:42,625
In that case, she could pretend like they got her.

95
00:10:53,988 --> 00:10:56,253
Let's go!

96
00:10:57,290 --> 00:10:59,481
Daddy!

97
00:11:00,494 --> 00:11:02,497
Were you a good boy?

98
00:11:02,556 --> 00:11:04,700
Where is Mommy?

99
00:11:07,194 --> 00:11:10,631
Now, say goodbye to your hosts.

100
00:11:10,631 --> 00:11:12,491
Thank you for everything.

101
00:11:12,491 --> 00:11:15,476
I'll bring Mommy along next time.

102
00:11:15,476 --> 00:11:19,108
I'll see you, Hyeon Woo.

103
00:11:19,165 --> 00:11:20,884
- Let's go. 
 - Okay.

104
00:11:20,908 --> 00:11:23,022
We'll get going.

105
00:11:28,720 --> 00:11:31,580
- Take care. 
 - You, too.

106
00:11:34,983 --> 00:11:38,821
Is it okay to let him go just like that?

107
00:11:39,809 --> 00:11:44,059
His father came to pick him up. There is nothing we can do about it.

108
00:11:45,692 --> 00:11:50,346
Stay out of their business if you don't want any trouble.

109
00:13:22,638 --> 00:13:24,489
What are the reasons for your voluntary appearance today?

110
00:13:24,559 --> 00:13:26,637
Does this have to do with Director Yoon Jae Hee?

111
00:13:26,701 --> 00:13:28,685
Are you aware that the stock prices are swaying?

112
00:13:28,740 --> 00:13:31,403
What are the reasons for your voluntary appearance?

113
00:13:31,479 --> 00:13:34,588
Did Director Yoon tell you anything before the arrest?

114
00:14:20,531 --> 00:14:25,111
I'm sorry about what's happening right now.

115
00:14:27,679 --> 00:14:30,326
But of course,

116
00:14:30,326 --> 00:14:34,026
you never loved your stepmother, so…

117
00:14:34,671 --> 00:14:38,293
You know Jae Hee's only been using you, right?

118
00:14:38,293 --> 00:14:41,706
I know she had to give your mother the choice over the CIO directorship

119
00:14:41,706 --> 00:14:43,739
and raise funds for your–

120
00:14:43,739 --> 00:14:45,855
Is that what she said?

121
00:14:46,980 --> 00:14:50,044
It is true that Mother wanted control over the CIO.

122
00:14:50,044 --> 00:14:55,583
That would help her handle higher government officials.

123
00:14:55,583 --> 00:15:01,233
Anyway, it doesn't matter who's the director as long as she's the one in control.

124
00:15:01,233 --> 00:15:03,093
Don't you agree?

125
00:15:08,812 --> 00:15:15,617
My wife had a phone call with No Young Joo the night she committed suicide.

126
00:15:18,207 --> 00:15:20,397
I'm sure you already know

127
00:15:20,397 --> 00:15:24,326
who No Young Joo was and how she died.

128
00:15:27,968 --> 00:15:33,196
But to have a phone call with someone who'd been dead for a month…

129
00:15:36,393 --> 00:15:41,201
There are not many that can arrange such a thing.

130
00:15:43,082 --> 00:15:48,059
Save your wife and free yourself from the Sungjin family.

131
00:15:48,059 --> 00:15:52,521
They never treat you properly as a family member, anyway.

132
00:15:55,919 --> 00:15:59,715
If you help me take down your stepmother,

133
00:15:59,715 --> 00:16:06,099
I'll persuade your wife so that you two can start over.

134
00:16:09,598 --> 00:16:12,150
A stepmother is also a mother.

135
00:16:12,150 --> 00:16:15,589
Are you telling me to betray my own mother?

136
00:16:15,589 --> 00:16:17,513
That's low.

137
00:16:20,499 --> 00:16:23,626
You're not doing all this just to help Jae Hee.

138
00:16:23,626 --> 00:16:25,890
What do you want?

139
00:16:25,890 --> 00:16:29,407
The secret files of the Sungjin family?

140
00:16:33,111 --> 00:16:35,400
Have some conscience.

141
00:16:35,400 --> 00:16:39,030
It's a real shame that you're using your dead wife's name in this.

142
00:16:40,166 --> 00:16:43,100
- You little punk! 
 - Think about it.

143
00:16:43,100 --> 00:16:46,039
Take the time and think about your decision

144
00:16:46,039 --> 00:16:49,592
to side with Jae Hee and against my mother.

145
00:16:49,592 --> 00:16:53,195
You'd better think carefully.

146
00:17:04,617 --> 00:17:06,800
I'll ask again.

147
00:17:08,312 --> 00:17:10,853
Did you admit to Yoon Jae Hee

148
00:17:10,853 --> 00:17:15,694
that you had ordered the murder of Kim Yi Seol?

149
00:17:24,444 --> 00:17:27,398
Hasn't it been 30 minutes? Since we started?

150
00:17:27,398 --> 00:17:28,921
Yes, Madam.

151
00:17:28,921 --> 00:17:31,823
It's been 37 minutes.

152
00:17:33,715 --> 00:17:36,809
I feel bad that your efforts will be in vain.

153
00:17:36,809 --> 00:17:40,457
There won't even be a trial for this.

154
00:17:40,457 --> 00:17:42,200
Are you scared?

155
00:17:43,435 --> 00:17:45,717
You will lose Hyeon Woo

156
00:17:45,717 --> 00:17:50,115
and be kicked out without a single penny for alimony.

157
00:17:50,115 --> 00:17:54,420
You will also pay for tampering with the reputation of the Sungjin family.

158
00:17:54,420 --> 00:18:00,738
You've killed many innocent people to acquire your wealth.

159
00:18:00,738 --> 00:18:05,198
And all of your crimes will be revealed.

160
00:18:06,828 --> 00:18:11,309
Good luck with everything.

161
00:18:13,218 --> 00:18:15,411
You'd better brace yourself.

162
00:18:16,099 --> 00:18:19,606
You have a lot of trouble coming your way.

163
00:18:34,546 --> 00:18:37,429
 How do you suggest I pay

164
00:18:37,429 --> 00:18:40,515
 for having Kim Yi Seol murdered?

165
00:18:42,038 --> 00:18:46,999
 To protect this family, I had Kim Yi Seol and No Young Joo murdered

166
00:18:46,999 --> 00:18:50,368
 and drove Kwon Min Seon to suicide.

167
00:18:50,368 --> 00:18:56,399
 I was also responsible for the deaths in the Hyeongsan-dong tragedy.

168
00:18:57,696 --> 00:18:59,596
 Tell me.

169
00:19:00,294 --> 00:19:05,388
 What should I do to pay for everything I've done?

170
00:19:07,895 --> 00:19:10,281
 Why are you doing this?

171
00:19:10,281 --> 00:19:15,063
 Are you saying such unspeakable things just to pressure him?

172
00:19:15,063 --> 00:19:17,617
 He wants to change.

173
00:19:17,617 --> 00:19:21,088
 Exactly how and how much do you want to change?

174
00:19:21,088 --> 00:19:25,566
 How will you pay for your own past wrongdoings?

175
00:19:25,566 --> 00:19:30,325
 If my methods are wrong, then how are yours going to be different?

176
00:19:33,511 --> 00:19:36,440
 You're not prepared to risk anything.

177
00:19:38,950 --> 00:19:41,497
 You should remember that

178
00:19:41,497 --> 00:19:45,056
 pointing out the wrong doesn't solve anything.

179
00:20:05,628 --> 00:20:08,495
Myeongseong Industries should

180
00:20:08,495 --> 00:20:12,936
back out from the demolition of Hyeongsan Area 5.

181
00:20:12,936 --> 00:20:14,956
What?

182
00:20:14,956 --> 00:20:18,106
You'll have to make five new corporate bodies.

183
00:20:18,106 --> 00:20:23,606
They will be the subcontractors in the demolition and divide up the area

184
00:20:23,606 --> 00:20:26,862
that Myeongseong is responsible for.

185
00:20:26,862 --> 00:20:28,704
What do you…

186
00:20:30,126 --> 00:20:33,193
Why would you make things so complicated?

187
00:20:33,193 --> 00:20:37,215
That way, should any issues come up regarding the demolition,

188
00:20:37,215 --> 00:20:40,356
Myeongseong Industries

189
00:20:40,356 --> 00:20:45,708
and Father will be free from any allegations.

190
00:20:50,056 --> 00:20:53,404
I'll get it done and report back to you.

191
00:21:58,122 --> 00:22:01,584
Why did you file for a review on legality of custody?

192
00:22:01,584 --> 00:22:05,021
Do you think it is fair that you're being released from custody?

193
00:22:05,021 --> 00:22:07,662
Why did you change your mind all of a sudden?

194
00:22:07,662 --> 00:22:10,412
How do you think it was possible for you to be released from custody?

195
00:22:10,412 --> 00:22:13,817
Is it true that you are not on good terms with each other?

196
00:22:13,817 --> 00:22:18,739
A review on the legality of custody is a right protected by law.

197
00:22:18,739 --> 00:22:22,780
Let me just say that it was the court's decision to temporarily

198
00:22:22,780 --> 00:22:26,610
release her from custody after a careful review of her charges.

199
00:22:26,610 --> 00:22:30,000
I'll be answering any further questions at a later time.

200
00:22:30,000 --> 00:22:32,127
Thank you for your understanding.

201
00:22:33,212 --> 00:22:35,320
Could you elaborate on the reasons behind this?

202
00:22:35,320 --> 00:22:38,590
One more comment, please.

203
00:22:48,290 --> 00:22:52,370
How can this even happen without me knowing?

204
00:22:53,337 --> 00:22:56,450
You decided to go against the family.

205
00:22:56,450 --> 00:22:59,010
And you know what we're capable of.

206
00:22:59,010 --> 00:23:00,722
You're pathetic.

207
00:23:06,343 --> 00:23:07,920
What about Hyeon Woo?

208
00:23:09,590 --> 00:23:12,030
Where's Hyeon Woo?

209
00:23:13,525 --> 00:23:17,670
Sir, are you rejoining Seo Han Sook?

210
00:23:18,105 --> 00:23:20,713
Remember who you're talking to.

211
00:23:20,713 --> 00:23:24,099
Why would you release Jae Hee like that if you're not joining them?

212
00:23:24,099 --> 00:23:27,887
The accused filed for it, and the court approved it, not me.

213
00:23:27,887 --> 00:23:30,749
You assigned another prosecutor on the case, didn't you?

214
00:23:30,749 --> 00:23:33,050
So that I wouldn't find out.

215
00:23:35,694 --> 00:23:39,317
Jung Joon Hyeok abandoned his wife and took Seo Han Sook's side.

216
00:23:39,317 --> 00:23:42,290
That bastard's determined.

217
00:23:44,209 --> 00:23:47,230
We can take a step back for now and wait.

218
00:23:47,230 --> 00:23:49,428
And when we see a chance

219
00:23:49,428 --> 00:23:52,490
to actually win, we can try again.

220
00:23:53,405 --> 00:23:54,593
Think about it.

221
00:23:54,593 --> 00:23:57,703
I might be dead even before the fight begins.

222
00:23:57,703 --> 00:24:01,925
Then will the two of you fight them on your own?

223
00:24:08,108 --> 00:24:10,000
Listen, Jung Ho.

224
00:24:11,097 --> 00:24:13,097
It was Seo Han Sook

225
00:24:13,097 --> 00:24:17,292
that killed the woman who was my wife for 25 years.

226
00:24:17,292 --> 00:24:19,490
Do you still not trust me?

227
00:24:25,658 --> 00:24:27,492
Hyeon Woo!

228
00:24:27,492 --> 00:24:30,440
- Hyeon Woo! 
 - Hyeon Woo is not here.

229
00:24:31,150 --> 00:24:33,130
He's at the family home.

230
00:24:35,768 --> 00:24:37,850
Bring him back right now.

231
00:24:39,628 --> 00:24:41,350
He's my son.

232
00:24:43,245 --> 00:24:46,912
Did you think that you could keep Hyeon Woo?

233
00:24:53,183 --> 00:24:56,089
You don't deserve to be his father.

234
00:24:56,089 --> 00:24:57,631
What?

235
00:24:58,308 --> 00:25:00,973
Will you tell everyone that I raped Yi Seol

236
00:25:00,973 --> 00:25:03,076
so you can keep Hyeon Woo?

237
00:25:09,836 --> 00:25:13,308
You couldn't go that far. You're his mother.

238
00:25:14,297 --> 00:25:17,297
So just keep quiet and wait.

239
00:25:17,297 --> 00:25:19,320
I'll give you the divorce.

240
00:25:42,399 --> 00:25:45,124
Stop, the two of you.

241
00:25:45,124 --> 00:25:47,590
We need to be discussing what's happening,

242
00:25:47,590 --> 00:25:51,016
and what we're going to do about it.

243
00:25:52,537 --> 00:25:58,004
So is Jung Joon Hyeok going against Madam Seo

244
00:25:58,049 --> 00:26:01,522
in order to protect Yoon Jae Hee?

245
00:26:01,522 --> 00:26:03,657
That cannot be the case.

246
00:26:03,657 --> 00:26:05,600
Then...

247
00:26:05,611 --> 00:26:12,306
Is Madam Seo forgiving Yoon Jae Hee to protect Sungjin?

248
00:26:12,306 --> 00:26:15,797
Madam Seo is never so benign.

249
00:26:15,813 --> 00:26:17,880
But it is certain that

250
00:26:17,880 --> 00:26:21,197
Cho Kang Hyeon has taken a step back.

251
00:26:24,292 --> 00:26:28,020
So what do we have to do now?

252
00:27:00,306 --> 00:27:02,405
Did you call for me, Mr. Jung?

253
00:27:02,407 --> 00:27:05,118
Welcome. Take a seat.

254
00:27:10,819 --> 00:27:13,458
Have you heard the news?

255
00:27:13,458 --> 00:27:17,508
I did, about your wife.

256
00:27:17,508 --> 00:27:20,380
How do you think everything will go from now on?

257
00:27:22,168 --> 00:27:25,379
Well, my duty is to follow your orders,

258
00:27:25,379 --> 00:27:28,980
- so I only– 
 - Exactly.

259
00:27:37,489 --> 00:27:43,408
